s://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/charli_green_vincent-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/charli_green_vincent-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">St. Vincent</a>已被确认为今晚<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖的</a>颁奖嘉宾。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="340" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-here-are-all-the-nominees-3576382"><b>2024 年全英音乐奖：以下是所有提名者</b></a></li></ul><p>颁奖典礼将于今晚（3 月 2 日）在伦敦 O2 剧场举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maya-jama-among-the-new-hosts-for-the-brit-awards-2024-3581190">由玛雅·贾玛 (Maya Jama)、克拉拉·阿姆福 (Clara Amfo) 和罗曼·坎普 (Roman Kemp) 三位主持人主持</a>。该赛事可在 ITV1 和 ITVX 上观看。</p><p>圣文森特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-interview-broken-man-dave-grohl-new-album-all-born-screaming-listen-3594747">本周宣布了她的新专辑《All Born Screaming》</a> ，她将在全英红地毯秀上为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》</a>颁发全英新星奖，该秀将由 ITV2 现场直播。 </p><figure id="attachment_3595743" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3595743" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3595743" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024.jpg" alt="（JM Enternational 2024 摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-conten