节目历史上获得提名最多的单一艺术家。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gorillaz">戈里拉兹</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-david">克雷格·大卫</a>此前保持着六项提名的纪录。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-here-are-all-the-nominees-3576382">她在回应这一消息时表示：</a> “就行业而言，我陷入了困境。在我最疯狂的梦想中，我从来没有想过再次尝试意味着获得七项全英音乐奖提名。这是完全不同的事情。最佳专辑？你生病了吗？”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-confirmed-to-perform-at-2024-brit-awards-3579216">这位出生于图廷的歌手</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-confirmed-to-perform-at-2024-brit-awards-3579216">将在全英音乐奖</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-becky-hill-and-chase-status-collab-performance-3588553">贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 和 Chase &amp; Status、杜阿·利帕 (</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> )、雷伊 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-confirmed-to-perform-at-2024-brit-awards-3579216">Raye</a> )、凯莉· <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-to-receive-brits-global-icon-award-and-perform-at-ceremony-3586464">米洛 (Kylie Minogue)（也将获得全英音乐奖全球偶像奖）</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">丛林 (Jungle</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rema">雷玛 (Rema)</a>上表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-here-are-all-the-nominees-3576382" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请在此处查看 2024 年全英音乐奖提名的完整列表</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vick-hope-mastercard-brits-awards-school-trailblazers-diversity-inclusion-technology-3590043">DJ Vick Hope 开启“为下一代拓宽音乐渠道”的对话的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
